OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSocial care: Official      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadvisers want immigration  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frules to be eased          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has been urged by its   
OL,6, official immigration advisers to make  
OL,7, it easier for foreign care workers to  
OL,8, come to the UK.                        
OL,10,FThe Migration Advisory Committee (MAC) 
OL,11,Fsaid the sector was facing "severe and 
OL,12,Fincreasing" problems with hiring and   
OL,13,Fretaining staff after Brexit.          
OL,15,FIt suggested changes to allow employers
OL,16,Fto sponsor visas for workers on more   
OL,17,Fthan #20,480 a year.                   
OL,19,FThe Home Office said it would consider 
OL,20,Fthe recommendation carefully.          
